Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina was deeply troubled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fried chicken and rolled omelette\Nshould be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe sweet and spicy kinpira...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! No brown colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}PAT PAT PAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It has to be a cute lunch, or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you open it,\Nit's like, "Ta-daaa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Wow, how cute!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a middle school boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's after a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would think "delicious-looking"\Nis better than "cute."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That was fast.\NYou peeled that many already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomorrow is Sunday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they're so neat.\NYou're good with your hands, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I asked you to come over.\NAfter all, I bought 4 kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The baseball team from Hina's\Nmiddle school is having a game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never eaten boiled chestnuts before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you can eat this inner brown skin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NYou have to boil it for a while, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It keeps well, so it's the perfect winter snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it seems the boy Hina is concerned about\Nwill be playing in the game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's the son of the milkman.\NThe tall boy named Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he drank\Nevery drop from his parent's milk shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:04.93,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was even shorter than Hina\Nback in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takahashi Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's the baseball team's ace\Nand the idol of Hina's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it seems Hina wants to give this boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}named Takahashi, who she's\Nconcerned about, a homemade lunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got more competition now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Hina's had a crush on Takahashi\Nsince elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I do not! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it like it's that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's the night before this young lady's\Nbig event, playing out before my very eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.72,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HmHm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.72,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Loves attentive work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:41.72,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crunch Crunch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I peel the skin off of chestnuts\Nthat are due to be boiled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkin croquettes shaped like apples\Nand a flower bed made of onigiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boil the pumpkin, mash it,\Nform it into balls, cover them with flour,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then coat them with egg yolk\Nand bread crumbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The game starts at 10, right?\NIf you leave the house at 9:30...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you make something\Nyou've never made before, I think it's risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know how long it'll take,\Nand it'll make you panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you panic, you'll make mistakes,\Nlike with the seasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, fried chicken, rolled omelette,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if you want something red,\Nmaybe cherry tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there anything I can eat, meow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way, that's too normal!\NIt's like an old woman's lunch! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Old woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.86,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! I'm going to decide on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.19,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harumph!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Go ahead, do what you want!\NI won't give you anymore advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thump Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nervous Nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maru S closes at 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-My money...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Empty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy all this,\Nbut I don't have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roll Roll
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chestnut pumpkin, ground beef,\Nbreadcrumbs, onions, eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}black pepper, radishes, olives,\Navocado, asparagus, baby corn,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}balsamic vinegar, lemons, mushroom,\Nred and yellow bell peppers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pet me some more! Purr, vroom, purr!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}king oyster mushrooms, fresh basil,\Ndecorative cups and toothpicks, rosemary...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you intend to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like,\Nhow much do you intend to spend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is not cost-effective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At a glance, this'll cost over 3,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a box lunch from a fancy restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to take 3,000 yen from\Nour food expenses for some other kid's lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we only buy milk\Nwhen it's on sale for 158 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Clench!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, you say "some other kid,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but aren't the cats and Kiriyama the same?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bloomph...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.72,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glossy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.72,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some other kids
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get to use up all the money\Non some other peoples' kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, are you someone else's kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?\NYou're not Momo's big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is awkward...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um... er... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, I'm the one who's sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I tried to pay for my share of the food before,\Nbut Akari wouldn't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But maybe now she will, starting with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then I won't feel so guilty about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhhh...\NSting Sting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis will pick up any kind of stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dogs, cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She always has. She can't ignore something\Nthat's just skin and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bark B... ark\NMeow Meow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, she likes to make them\Nsoft and fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I was surprised\Nwhen she brought a person home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay. I'm sure Sis will make you\Nsoft and fluffy in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. You'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}And then, Sunday morning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just rolled the croquettes into balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something's burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet apple sautee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sloppy Sloppy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's 8 already? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I woke up at 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, who is it? I'm busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}New Message\NYoko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, "I'm running late.\NPlease leave without me." There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}New Message\NSending
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}New Message\NSent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, that's right! What should I wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was so focused on lunch,\NI didn't think about my outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this too stylish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like I'm way too enthusiastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, I'm now late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Curtains and Carpets\NShimoda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Curtains are more expensive than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'll finally be able to sleep peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any matches for a while,\Nso this is a good opportunity to start
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,gathering things I need for the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I still need a chair, a desk, a bookshelf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina's middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's the rumored Takahashi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's so tall.\NIs he really a middle school student?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he certainly is cool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best! Smash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There she is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if she finished his lunch in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's a comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-Home run?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Takahashi! I love you!\N- You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've always loved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- He did it!\N- Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-So cool...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really hit it out of the park...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He totally looks like a main character\Nfrom a shonen manga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen Hina\Nwith that expression before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It really looks like springtime in her life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a bittersweet feeling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or like she's in love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get dressed, and we'll meet at Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For monja? I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is Takahashi around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming, right, Takahashi?\NTo Matsuda's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}- You were so cool!\N- Great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You're going to Matsuda?\N- Can we come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Monja it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm starving.\N- Come on, Takahashi, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, Sis will ask me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll ask me why I didn't give it to him,\Nafter all that trouble I went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis won't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is she crying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's good at cooking, and I'm sure anyone\Nwould be happy to have a bento she made...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yesterday evening and even just now,\Nshe looked so happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.\NLet's go home and eat it with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't understand women.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You couldn't give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You worked so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't cry. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happened to me before, too.\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You weren't able\Nto give a lunch you made, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, just like you, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make a cute lunch\Nand I got so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard, but I panicked,\Nand then I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.82,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.82,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harumph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I couldn't help but say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But later on, I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I said to you last night\Nis what Mom told me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like mother, like daughter,\NI guess you could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's eat it with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What? Do you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Really? I can? Hom nom nom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay, the tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh? What happened to the kitties?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maybe they were so full they got sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, did you taste this beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was something bitter, sweet, and sour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It indeed tasted like the end of a first love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, let's do some training together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah. I'll do my best next time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's a good thing\Nthat she wasn't able to deliver her first bento.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what Kiriyama and I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.99,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:35.00,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V. S.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm the one who won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You could say that, as a phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phenomenon... But it's reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I know. Fine, you "won."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what makes you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're objecting,\Nlike, "Yeah, yeah, it can't be helped."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more time. I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with a static rook\Nand you do the bishop exchange once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?\NIt's like I'm a practice board!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's petty! You're being petty, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This matter is urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With the bishop exchange,\NI can't let you have everything your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should use the ranging rook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like using the static rook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you have me use a strategy\NI'm not good at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ugh—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, geez. How many times have I told you\Nthat studying alone suits me better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As rivals, we raise each other up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so losing this precious rivalry\Nwould be a major loss to your shogi life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do understand that, don't you, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At times, haste is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying the two of us need to find it,\Nwithout a moment to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, you're the one who has to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The "bishop exchange crusher" silver bullet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.29,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Nikaidou vaccine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ga-blam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it'd be the "Kiriyama Vaccine"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I've dreamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The "Nikaidou Vaccine"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or the "Nikaidou System"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To leave a technique with my name\Nfor the next generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand... but I'd rather not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You suddenly show up at 9 in the morning,\Ntalking about developing a "silver bullet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I'm an "all-rounder,"\Nso I have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rumble
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rumble Groggle Grumble
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... get some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, yeah. How about MecBurger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GigaMec\N#1 Burger
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably like the GigaMec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GigaMec...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MecBurger
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you always eat, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm alone, I eat bread, Smiley's Bento,\NMec's, or Yoshidaya's beef bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, I sometimes have dinner\Nat an acquaintance's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Where are your sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Quiver Quiver Quiver
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.13,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Whump
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded like this one yelled "Bodoro" at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bodoro is that one character...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The super-popular anime masterpiece\Nloved by children, adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and yours truly, about an intelligent being\Nwho lives in the mysterious forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bodoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do feel a deep connection\Nto that character's intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, little one.\NI shall ask you your name. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, Momo. Shall we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Traffic is dangerous here\Nwith all the cars going to and fro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bodoro, Bodoro! Bododo, bododo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Momo seems so happy.\NMore than when she's with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where do you live? I shall walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There she is. Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's with Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Rei, who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Akari? Your face is really red.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me Akari has a weakness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...for that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, he's, uh...\NFrom shogi... I mean, my club...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kiriyama's best friend,\NHarunobu Nikaidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Have you had dinner?\NYou should come over as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:51.46,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fidget    Fidget
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sis, someone else's kid again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such kind words. It would be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Bodoro! Fold some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an old house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like a movie set.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay. Nothing for you to apologize, Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Plump Plump
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}#1 in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Bloomph
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Gold
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Round and shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thump Thump Thump Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say, your wonderful friend\Nis just like a nice, round, shiny ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like a ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard anyone\Ndescribe a friend like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.\NSis is extremely fond of soft and fluffy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We went grocery shopping today,\Nso I can make pretty much anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fried chicken? Salisbury steak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salisb... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you could make something\Nbland and light on protein...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I'm sorry. It's nothing. I can eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual. You prefer a mature taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's odd. It's impossible to maintain\Na plump body like that with such a strict menu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thump Thump Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he on a diet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not good. If he diets,\Nthat beautiful ball-like shine would...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, but I see, I would worry about it, too.\NHe is around that age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fat\NSugar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A slow metabolism...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or maybe the situation is even more serious?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how appealingly soft and fluffy he is,\Nit won't mean a thing unless he's healthy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's okay! Leave it to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delicious.\NSorry for your trouble, Akari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You promised you wouldn't say that,\Nremember?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I hate to say it, Akari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}But I can't have melon or bamboo shoots.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Lots of Money
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what to eat these days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't even enjoy booze.\NThey said I could have just a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Poor Mr. Yamamoto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, I'll look into mild-tasting snacks for you.\NI'll search the internet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I didn't take care of Grandma, and listen\Nto my customers at the club just for show!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Season it as you like, Nikaidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! Even though it's bland...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. Chew well and eat slowly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.95,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got hooked in,\Nand also chewing well
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My butler is always telling me\Nto chew each bite at least 30 times,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm always too impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a kind butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not being cared for by Akari,\Nso somewhat sad beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who it could be at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry to disturb you so late this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Young Master\Nhas been enjoying your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hanaoka. Are you here to pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're Nikaidou's...\NI'm surprised you found your way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I used a GPS—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me! My lungs are a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I happened to be passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He always comes to pick me up,\Nno matter where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been like that. Like magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Heh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:21.38,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeeek
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second, Nikaidou.\NYou're totally under surveillance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He just said GPS. He definitely said it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you'd like, please enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the neighborhood,\Nso you may already know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this is one of my favorite sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a coincidence.\NI love these sweets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MIKAZUKI-DOU
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, won't you come in and have these with us?\NI'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you don't mind. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, would you boil some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V. S.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.97,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.30,0:24:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was my dad's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.97,0:24:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's an adult,\Nhe really talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.44,0:24:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.36,0:24:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.07,0:24:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion," too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.82,0:24:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I won't mess up\Nthe next bento!